Hello Sujith,

Thank you for getting back to us.

In the first screenshot it appears that the site doesn't have a certificate assigned, could you please check if that is the case ? 

Also verify if the certificate is either signed by us or by a trusted authority.

Regarding the default templates for CAP policies, they can be created under the EPP UI -> System parameters -> Device Types and Notifications.


Have a nice day ahead!

Best regards,
__________________
